	<item>
		<title>GroupMappers, MORU, is featured in celebration of World Malaria Day 2023 by WHO news.</title>
		<link>https://groupmappers.com/2023/07/25/groupmappers-moru-is-featured-in-celebration-of-world-malaria-day-2023-by-who-news/</link>
					<comments>https://groupmappers.com/2023/07/25/groupmappers-moru-is-featured-in-celebration-of-world-malaria-day-2023-by-who-news/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 25 Jul 2023 09:47:16 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://groupmappers.com/?p=12485</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Who doesn&#8217;t love being acknowledged on the global stage? GroupMappers, MORU, is featured in celebration of World Malaria Day 2023 by WHO news. Check out the link below to read all about the malaria elimination efforts in Bangladesh!�� https://www.who.int/bangladesh/news/detail/05-07-2023-celebration-of-world-malaria-day-2023Thanks to the National Malaria Elimination Programme of Bangladesh for arranging this valuable event.]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="12485" class="elementor elementor-12485">
						<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-6f023be elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="6f023be" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-d4270ee" data-id="d4270ee" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3d3a791 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="3d3a791" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<div class="xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">Who doesn&#8217;t love being acknowledged on the global stage?</div>
</div>
<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto"><span class="x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xhhsvwb xat24cr xgzva0m xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od"><img decoding="async" src="https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tbe/1/16/1f3c6.png" alt="&#x1f3c6;" width="16" height="16" /></span> GroupMappers, MORU, is featured in celebration of World Malaria Day 2023 by WHO news. <span class="x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xhhsvwb xat24cr xgzva0m xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od"><img decoding="async" src="https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t3f/1/16/1f30d.png" alt="&#x1f30d;" width="16" height="16" /></span><span class="x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xhhsvwb xat24cr xgzva0m xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od"><img decoding="async" src="https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t5e/1/16/1f99f.png" alt="&#x1f99f;" width="16" height="16" /></span></div>
</div>
<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">Check out the link below to read all about the malaria elimination efforts in Bangladesh!</div>
<div dir="auto"><span class="x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xhhsvwb xat24cr xgzva0m xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t51/1/16/1f449.png" alt="&#x1f449;" width="16" height="16" /></span>�<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1fey0fg" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.who.int/bangladesh/news/detail/05-07-2023-celebration-of-world-malaria-day-2023?fbclid=IwAR28S9qfej-mP36_ACLCMRm8VFkS9gVrwRYpi0dKgsFNqOERaNAYMIpyvuk" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">� https://www.who.int/bangladesh/news/detail/05-07-2023-celebration-of-world-malaria-day-202</a>3</div>
</div>
<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">Thanks to the National Malaria Elimination Programme of Bangladesh for arranging this valuable event.</div>
</div>
