		<item>
		<title>Update on Monsoon Aedes Mosquito Survey</title>
		<link>https://groupmappers.com/2023/06/19/update-on-monsoon-aedes-mosquito-survey/</link>
					<comments>https://groupmappers.com/2023/06/19/update-on-monsoon-aedes-mosquito-survey/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 19 Jun 2023 13:28:37 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://groupmappers.com/?p=12450</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[As part of year long activities the National Malaria Elimination and Aedes Transmitted Disease Control Program effectively carried out the Monsoon Aedes Survey.The goal of this study was to collect vector data for micro-level planning to deal with dengue outbreaks.GroupMappers is pleased to have contributed to this significant initiative. We are working together to provide]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="12450" class="elementor elementor-12450">
						<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c6ce54c elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="c6ce54c" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-76d8fbd" data-id="76d8fbd" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6b82402 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="6b82402" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">As part of year long activities the National Malaria Elimination and Aedes Transmitted Disease Control Program effectively carried out the Monsoon Aedes Survey.</div>
</div>
<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">The goal of this study was to collect vector data for micro-level planning to deal with dengue outbreaks.</div>
</div>
<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">GroupMappers is pleased to have contributed to this significant initiative. We are working together to provide the authorities with crucial information to tackle dengue during the monsoon season.</div>
</div>
<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">As the alarming cases of dengue continue to rise, let&#8217;s prioritize the cleanliness of our neighborhoods and utilize mosquito repellents and bed nets to ensure the safety and well-being of everyone.</div>
</div>
								</div>
				</div>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-020632d elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="020632d" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
