		<item>
		<title>NMEP, BRAC, and GroupMappers unite to celebrate The World Malaria Day, 2023</title>
		<link>https://groupmappers.com/2023/06/15/nmep-brac-and-groupmappers-unite-to-celebrate-the-world-malaria-day-2023/</link>
					<comments>https://groupmappers.com/2023/06/15/nmep-brac-and-groupmappers-unite-to-celebrate-the-world-malaria-day-2023/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 15 Jun 2023 06:56:23 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://groupmappers.com/?p=12403</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[NMEP, BRAC, and GroupMappers unite to celebrate The World Malaria Day, 2023. Honorable Health Minister Zahid Malek, alongside esteemed officials including CDC and DGHS Directors, grace the event.Together, we&#8217;re making significant strides in the fight against malaria.GroupMappers&#8217; innovative surveillance dashboard enhances monitoring efforts, providing real-time insights for effective resource distribution and healthcare worker deployment.Let&#8217;s raise]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="12403" class="elementor elementor-12403">
						<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-ad96304 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="ad96304" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-03f34ae" data-id="03f34ae" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a90480f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="a90480f" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<div class="xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">NMEP, BRAC, and GroupMappers unite to celebrate The World Malaria Day, 2023. Honorable Health Minister Zahid Malek, alongside esteemed officials including CDC and DGHS Directors, grace the event.</div>
</div>
<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">Together, we&#8217;re making significant strides in the fight against malaria.</div>
</div>
<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">GroupMappers&#8217; innovative surveillance dashboard enhances monitoring efforts, providing real-time insights for effective resource distribution and healthcare worker deployment.</div>
</div>
<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">Let&#8217;s raise awareness, commemorate progress, and reaffirm our commitment to a malaria-free future.</div>
</div>
<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">Join us as we work towards a world without malaria.</div>
</div>
								</div>
				</div>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-8dd7e4b elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="8dd7e4b" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-c9f0dbb" data-id="c9f0dbb" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-704baec elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="704baec" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
