		<item>
		<title>Workshop on Development of Malaria funding request to Global Fund (GC-7)</title>
		<link>https://groupmappers.com/2023/02/26/workshop-on-development-of-malaria-funding-request-to-global-fund-gc-7/</link>
					<comments>https://groupmappers.com/2023/02/26/workshop-on-development-of-malaria-funding-request-to-global-fund-gc-7/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 26 Feb 2023 12:33:54 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://groupmappers.com/?p=10911</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[GroupMappers had the privilege of attending the “Workshop on Development of Malaria funding request to Global Fund (GC-7)”, organized by the National Malaria Elimination and Aedes Transmission Control Program of the Directorate General of Health Services (DGHS), Ministry of Health and Family Welfare (MoH&#38;FW), supported by the World Health Organization (WHO).Our team, along with BRAC]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="10911" class="elementor elementor-10911">
						<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-fe85e51 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="fe85e51" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-7a63b50" data-id="7a63b50" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-db5465d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="db5465d" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>GroupMappers had the privilege of attending the “Workshop on Development of Malaria funding request to Global Fund (GC-7)”, organized by the National Malaria Elimination and Aedes Transmission Control Program of the Directorate General of Health Services (DGHS), Ministry of Health and Family Welfare (MoH&amp;FW), supported by the World Health Organization (WHO).<br />Our team, along with BRAC Consortium and WHO, joined hands to discuss advancing malaria control efforts in Bangladesh with SMART Surveillance. At the workshop, we showcased how GroupMappers is assisting the NMEP (National Malaria Elimination Program) to collect micro stratified malaria data from villages. This data will help the program to make better interventions and have strong surveillance towards malaria elimination.<br />We are proud to be a part of this initiative and working towards a malaria-free Bangladesh.</p>
								</div>
				</div>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-c5837fc elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="c5837fc" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-9e3efc6" data-id="9e3efc6" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f4ea1b0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="f4ea1b0" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
															<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="768" src="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/E88DC258-35FA-4175-B8E2-42A08B82ABD0-1024x768.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-10914" alt="" srcset="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/E88DC258-35FA-4175-B8E2-42A08B82ABD0-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/E88DC258-35FA-4175-B8E2-42A08B82ABD0-300x225.jpg 300w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/E88DC258-35FA-4175-B8E2-42A08B82ABD0-768x576.jpg 768w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/E88DC258-35FA-4175-B8E2-42A08B82ABD0-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/E88DC258-35FA-4175-B8E2-42A08B82ABD0-900x675.jpg 900w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/E88DC258-35FA-4175-B8E2-42A08B82ABD0-600x450.jpg 600w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/E88DC258-35FA-4175-B8E2-42A08B82ABD0.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
				<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-799125d" data-id="799125d" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6690762 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="6690762" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
															<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="768" src="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/1107267C-2E14-4632-B574-B9A6C127B330-1024x768.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-10915" alt="" srcset="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/1107267C-2E14-4632-B574-B9A6C127B330-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/1107267C-2E14-4632-B574-B9A6C127B330-300x225.jpg 300w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/1107267C-2E14-4632-B574-B9A6C127B330-768x576.jpg 768w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/1107267C-2E14-4632-B574-B9A6C127B330-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/1107267C-2E14-4632-B574-B9A6C127B330-900x675.jpg 900w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/1107267C-2E14-4632-B574-B9A6C127B330-600x450.jpg 600w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/1107267C-2E14-4632-B574-B9A6C127B330.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															</div>
				</div>
