		<item>
		<title>Updates on Crisis Ready Project (CRP) workshop!</title>
		<link>https://groupmappers.com/2023/02/10/updates-on-crisis-ready-project-crp-workshop/</link>
					<comments>https://groupmappers.com/2023/02/10/updates-on-crisis-ready-project-crp-workshop/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 10 Feb 2023 05:13:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://groupmappers.com/?p=10470</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Our CRP workshop has been successfully completed on the topic of “Use of Mobility Data for Guiding Public Health Responses”. The workshop took place in Thailand on February 9 and 10, 2023.The workshop&#8217;s main purpose was to use mobility data for public health purposes.]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="10470" class="elementor elementor-10470">
						<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2e36342 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="2e36342" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-ed97191" data-id="ed97191" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ce88606 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ce88606" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">Our CRP workshop has been successfully completed on the topic of “Use of Mobility Data for Guiding Public Health Responses”. </div>
<div dir="auto">The workshop took place in Thailand on February 9 and 10, 2023.</div>
</div>
<div class="x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a">
<div dir="auto">The workshop&#8217;s main purpose was to use mobility data for public health purposes.</div>
</div>
								</div>
				</div>
