		<item>
		<title>Implementing village level data collection and surveillance towards malaria elimination</title>
		<link>https://groupmappers.com/2023/01/11/technical-assistance-in-implementing-village-level-data-collection-and-surveillance-towards-malaria-elimination-in-lama-upazila-bandarban/</link>
					<comments>https://groupmappers.com/2023/01/11/technical-assistance-in-implementing-village-level-data-collection-and-surveillance-towards-malaria-elimination-in-lama-upazila-bandarban/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 11 Jan 2023 06:02:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://groupmappers.com/?p=9476</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Our five-day training session in Lama, Bandarban, has completed successfully on &#8220;Technical assistance in implementing village level data collection and surveillance towards malaria elimination in Lama upazila, Bandarban”. In Bandarban&#8217;s Lama Upazila, we taught healthcare workers from these unions- Fasiyakhali, Faitang, Gajalia, Serai, Ruposhipara, and Lama upazila.Health workers learned to send malaria data using the]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="9476" class="elementor elementor-9476">
						<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-446fdf0 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="446fdf0" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-6b04ae0" data-id="6b04ae0" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9d47a48 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="9d47a48" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Our five-day training session in Lama, Bandarban, has completed successfully on &#8220;Technical assistance in implementing village level data collection and surveillance towards malaria elimination in Lama upazila, Bandarban”. <br />In Bandarban&#8217;s Lama Upazila, we taught healthcare workers from these unions- Fasiyakhali, Faitang, Gajalia, Serai, Ruposhipara, and Lama upazila.<br />Health workers learned to send malaria data using the USSD system and kobo toolbox. To make it possible, a lot of support was provided by our field crew. <br />The Lama local authority also helped us out with the events.<br />We appreciate MORU and APMEN&#8217;s assistance and financial contribution to the training</p>
								</div>
				</div>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-49d9ddc elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="49d9ddc" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
