		<item>
		<title>Assisting in introduction of G6PD testing to improve malaria treatment in Bangladesh.</title>
		<link>https://groupmappers.com/2022/12/15/a-two-day-workshop-with-find-iccdr-b-and-nmep-on-applying-diagnostic-network-optimisation-analysis-to-inform-the-introduction-of-g6pd-testing-into-bangladesh-for-improved-malaria-treatment-was/</link>
					<comments>https://groupmappers.com/2022/12/15/a-two-day-workshop-with-find-iccdr-b-and-nmep-on-applying-diagnostic-network-optimisation-analysis-to-inform-the-introduction-of-g6pd-testing-into-bangladesh-for-improved-malaria-treatment-was/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Thu, 15 Dec 2022 05:28:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://groupmappers.com/?p=9420</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[A two-day workshop with FiND , ICCDR, B and NMEP on &#8220;Applying Diagnostic Network Optimisation Analysis&#8221; to inform the introduction of G6PD testing into Bangladesh for improved malaria treatment was held on December 14th and 15th, 2022. The project’s aim was to support the National Malaria Elimination Program (NMEP) in Bangladesh by modeling an evidence-based]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="9420" class="elementor elementor-9420">
						<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-82a5d2f elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="82a5d2f" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-ea15db5" data-id="ea15db5" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-dd6f5a4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="dd6f5a4" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>A two-day workshop with FiND , ICCDR, B and NMEP on &#8220;Applying Diagnostic Network Optimisation Analysis&#8221; to inform the introduction of G6PD testing into Bangladesh for improved malaria treatment was held on December 14th and 15th, 2022. <br />The project’s aim was to support the National Malaria Elimination Program (NMEP) in Bangladesh by modeling an evidence-based strategy for introducing G6PD diagnosis that best uses available resources to ensure optimal access to testing by P. vivax patients and running the OptiDx baseline model to estimate the coverage and cost of potential scenarios for G6PD testing</p>
								</div>
				</div>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-1f66561 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="1f66561" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-5240f43" data-id="5240f43" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e07fe21 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="e07fe21" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
															<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="623" src="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320811567_523192509756883_5078948741165636619_n-1024x623.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-9423" alt="" srcset="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320811567_523192509756883_5078948741165636619_n-1024x623.jpg 1024w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320811567_523192509756883_5078948741165636619_n-300x182.jpg 300w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320811567_523192509756883_5078948741165636619_n-768x467.jpg 768w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320811567_523192509756883_5078948741165636619_n-1536x934.jpg 1536w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320811567_523192509756883_5078948741165636619_n-900x547.jpg 900w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320811567_523192509756883_5078948741165636619_n-600x365.jpg 600w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320811567_523192509756883_5078948741165636619_n.jpg 1557w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d4e9506 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="d4e9506" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
															<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="770" src="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320437920_3497013470528431_1698111513583127688_n-1024x770.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-9425" alt="" srcset="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320437920_3497013470528431_1698111513583127688_n-1024x770.jpg 1024w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320437920_3497013470528431_1698111513583127688_n-300x226.jpg 300w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320437920_3497013470528431_1698111513583127688_n-768x577.jpg 768w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320437920_3497013470528431_1698111513583127688_n-900x677.jpg 900w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320437920_3497013470528431_1698111513583127688_n-600x451.jpg 600w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/320437920_3497013470528431_1698111513583127688_n.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
				<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-464e193" data-id="464e193" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-721e78a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="721e78a" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
