		<item>
		<title>Mass Dog Vaccination Program (MDV)</title>
		<link>https://groupmappers.com/2022/12/05/mass-dog-vaccination-program-mdv-from-30th-november-to-5th-december-2022/</link>
					<comments>https://groupmappers.com/2022/12/05/mass-dog-vaccination-program-mdv-from-30th-november-to-5th-december-2022/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 05 Dec 2022 05:42:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://groupmappers.com/?p=9439</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[&#8220;Mass Dog Vaccination Program (MDV)&#8221; from 30th November to 5th December, 2022The five-day-long &#8220;Mass Dog Vaccination (MDV)&#8221; under the National Rabies Control and Elimination Program, CDC, ZDCP and DGHS has begun yesterday, November 30th, in both Dhaka City Corporations, following the nationwide program. This is the third round of mass vaccination for all owned and]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="9439" class="elementor elementor-9439">
						<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-9d1aa80 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="9d1aa80" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-604506f" data-id="604506f" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7faec4a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="7faec4a" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>&#8220;Mass Dog Vaccination Program (MDV)&#8221; from 30th November to 5th December, 2022<br />The five-day-long &#8220;Mass Dog Vaccination (MDV)&#8221; under the National Rabies Control and Elimination Program, CDC, ZDCP and DGHS has begun yesterday, November 30th, in both Dhaka City Corporations, following the nationwide program. <br />This is the third round of mass vaccination for all owned and stray dogs, with the goal of attaining herd immunity in the dog population. <br />GroupMappers has been providing assistance to this program to support the field based data collection, training, monitoring, reporting and analysis to accelerate the elimination of rabies from Bangladesh since February of 2018.<br />GroupMappers is strongly committed to reducing the risk of fatal diseases such as rabies, and we would like to offer our sincere appreciation to the DGHS for providing us with such a wonderful opportunity and our super energetic volunteer team to work for animal welfare.</p>
								</div>
				</div>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-ae930f5 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="ae930f5" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
