		<item>
		<title>Celebrating GIS Day, 2022 with JnU</title>
		<link>https://groupmappers.com/2022/11/20/our-training-in-lama-upazila-is-continuing-this-week-under-technical-assistance-in-implementing-village-level-data-collection-and-surveillance-towards-malaria-elimination-at-lama-bandarban/</link>
					<comments>https://groupmappers.com/2022/11/20/our-training-in-lama-upazila-is-continuing-this-week-under-technical-assistance-in-implementing-village-level-data-collection-and-surveillance-towards-malaria-elimination-at-lama-bandarban/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 20 Nov 2022 05:54:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://groupmappers.com/?p=9464</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Jagannath University celebrates GIS Day, 2022, with the theme &#8220;Share your passion and inspire the world!&#8221;Geography helps us understand our planet and interact with the world around us. It helps us figure out how things are, why they are where they are, and how cultural, economic, and political connections and movements affect us all.Therefore, GroupMappers&#8217;]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="9464" class="elementor elementor-9464">
						<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-efc94be elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="efc94be" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-e4aa65b" data-id="e4aa65b" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a9ba1e1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="a9ba1e1" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Jagannath University celebrates GIS Day, 2022, with the theme &#8220;Share your passion and inspire the world!&#8221;<br />Geography helps us understand our planet and interact with the world around us. It helps us figure out how things are, why they are where they are, and how cultural, economic, and political connections and movements affect us all.<br />Therefore, GroupMappers&#8217; principal objective is to maintain a geospatial perspective in order to see and work through problems.<br />Shout out to Jagannath University&#8217;s Geography and Environment Department for celebrating GIS Day with such enthusiasm and for getting students and teachers involved in spreading the power of GIS. <br />It gives us great pleasure to be able to sponsor the young team of JnU. <br />To encourage the volunteers, Mr. Sazid Ibna Zaman, co-founder of GroupMappers, Mr. Mohammad Abdul Hadi, Country Manager at Esri Bangladesh/Esri South Asia, Vice-Chancellor of Jagannath University Professor Md. Imdadul Hoque, treasurer Professor Kamaluddin Ahmed and chairman Dr. Md Abdul Quader and other teachers from the department were present.</p>
								</div>
				</div>
				<section class="elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-6be6e6a elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="6be6e6a" data-element_type="section" data-e-type="section">
						<div class="elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default">
					<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-c6c2f9b" data-id="c6c2f9b" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d5835a2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="d5835a2" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
															<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="768" src="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316113518_3357919677812861_7216339683318669044_n-1024x768.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-9584" alt="" srcset="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316113518_3357919677812861_7216339683318669044_n-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316113518_3357919677812861_7216339683318669044_n-300x225.jpg 300w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316113518_3357919677812861_7216339683318669044_n-768x576.jpg 768w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316113518_3357919677812861_7216339683318669044_n-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316113518_3357919677812861_7216339683318669044_n-900x675.jpg 900w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316113518_3357919677812861_7216339683318669044_n-600x450.jpg 600w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316113518_3357919677812861_7216339683318669044_n.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															</div>
				</div>
					</div>
		</div>
				<div class="elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-42822cc" data-id="42822cc" data-element_type="column" data-e-type="column">
			<div class="elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated">
						<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0720ded elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="0720ded" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
															<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="768" src="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316037169_3357919474479548_6259571720024836165_n-1024x768.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-9585" alt="" srcset="https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316037169_3357919474479548_6259571720024836165_n-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316037169_3357919474479548_6259571720024836165_n-300x225.jpg 300w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316037169_3357919474479548_6259571720024836165_n-768x576.jpg 768w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316037169_3357919474479548_6259571720024836165_n-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316037169_3357919474479548_6259571720024836165_n-900x675.jpg 900w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316037169_3357919474479548_6259571720024836165_n-600x450.jpg 600w, https://groupmappers.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/316037169_3357919474479548_6259571720024836165_n.jpg 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" />															</div>
				</div>
